<paragraph blockId="55.[151,1437,892,1208]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
Note: Before being described, this species was thought to be a form of 
<taxonomicName authority="Navas, 1924" authorityName="Navas" authorityYear="1924" box="[1004,1356,1109,1136]" class="Insecta" family="Coenagrionidae" genus="Oxyagrion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Odonata" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bruchi">
<emphasis box="[1004,1204,1109,1136]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Oxyagrion bruchi</emphasis>
